Interface GenericAbstractFiniteMetricSpace<T>

All Superinterfaces:
GenericAbstractMetricSpace<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
EuclideanMetricSpace, GenericFiniteMetricSpace
public interface GenericAbstractFiniteMetricSpace<T>
extends GenericAbstractMetricSpace<T>

This class abstracts the functionality of a finite metric space. The elements are indexed by the integers {0, ..., n - 1}, where n is the size of the metric space.

Author:
Andrew Tausz
